With brightness memory, you can retain your preferred brightness settings, providing you with a more convenient and personalized lighting experience. Let the light adapt to your lifestyle intelligently and bring enhanced comfort to your daily life.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, attractive minimalist lamp with a long battery life but not really bright enough to read by
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to keep by my meditation chair for occasional reading and also to take it out on my porch in the summer since it's supposed to be waterproof. But it's not really bright enough to read by unless you hold it directly over your book, and who wants to do that. It's more of an ambiance light... and it's good for when you wake up in the night and need to do something complicated, like reset your electric heater for an hour (turn on, turn to low, oscillate, set for one hour - no matter how well I learn where the buttons are, I can't do this in the dark in the middle of the night!). It's very stylish and the base is heavy, so it's sturdy... and I've been using it for a few minutes every day for several weeks and it is going strong. I like the touch factor and having the warm light option as well as the other cool and bright light options.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This lamp is so modern and looks so good!
reviews.reviewText: I love my thin stainless steel accent lamp by JALVDE! It looks so cool up on my bookcase shelf, and it illuminates the whole area because of the super bright LED's.
